            <html:p>A <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-0033.xml" title="carrable map" addr="jms-0033" type="local">carrable map</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{E}\xrightarrow {{p}}{B}]]></fr:tex> in a category <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex> is said to be <html:em>exponentiable</html:em> when it is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-0032.xml" title="exponentiable object" addr="jms-0032" type="local">exponentiable</fr:link> when viewed as an object of the slice category <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathcal {C}}_{/B}]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
